Package com.amplifyframework.api.aws

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GraphQLRequestOptions
    Options to be provided to a AppSyncGraphQLRequest.Builder.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApiAuthProviders
    Wrapper class to contain Auth providers for API multi-auth support.
    ApiAuthProviders.Builder
    Static Builder class for conveniently constructing an immutable instance of ApiAuthProviders.
    ApiGraphQLRequestOptions
    Defines options for building a GraphQLRequest when using the API category directly (DataStore is disabled).
    AppSyncGraphQLOperation<R>
    An operation to enqueue a GraphQL request to OkHttp client, with the goal of obtaining a list of responses.
    AppSyncGraphQLRequest<R>
    A request against an AppSync GraphQL endpoint.
    AppSyncGraphQLRequest.Builder
    Builder for a AppSyncGraphQLRequest.
    AppSyncGraphQLRequestFactory
    Converts provided model or class type into a request container with automatically generated GraphQL documents that follow AppSync specifications.
    AWSApiPlugin
    Plugin implementation to be registered with Amplify API category.
    AWSApiPluginConfiguration
    Configuration bundle for the AWS API plugin.
    AWSApiPluginConfiguration.Builder
    Constructs configuration objects through fluent method chaining.
    GsonVariablesSerializer
    Implementation of a GraphQL Request serializer for the variables map using Gson.
    SelectionSet
    Class representing a node of a SelectionSet for use in a GraphQLDocument.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuthorizationType
    The types of authorization one can use while talking to an Amazon AppSync GraphQL backend.
    EndpointType
    The type of API for a given endpoint.
    LeafSerializationBehavior
    Enum representing the different ways to serialize leaf nodes of a SelectionSet.
